data.name: lblWelcome.Text
data.value:
To begin, choose one of these Menu Items
SEARCH This allows you to look at the collection of images that have been cataloged in the Ranch Image Database FILE This contains a choice to allow you to EXIT the program or show settings.
SCANNED RECORDS This allows you to log information about newly scanned images or modify existing information.
KNOWLEDGE BASE This allows you to view the information or modify information stored in the Ranch Image Database about the persons shown in the pictures as well as create new Person records.
HELP This allows you to send questions or comments to a selected list of persons without the need to use another mail program (which you may still do). It also allows you to update this application to a new version.
